descriptionMarkdown:
This is a book combining all of [Nilaus'](https://factorioprints.com/user/4POMqXHwmtatNNqubcNRuFoCYml2) blueprints used in his Base-in-a-Book [Youtube series](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=1bWuYFzvXW4&list=PLV3rF--heRVs-s65QNxdGFMinlV-U53w6).

Combined for convenience in original form, all credit to Nilaus.

**Update 2022-03-20**: Fixes for latest version. Credit to Doug Bateman in the comments.

**Update 2019-01-09**: Added indicators for inputs and outputs using constant combinators. Minor icon / title changes.

**Update 2019-01-07**: Added the missing blueprints 13. Blue Science, Electric Mining Drills and Engines.
title: Nilaus' Base-in-a-Book complete
